  9:{title:"Completion, Compassion & Universal Service",theme:"The most expansive pinnacle — a time of culmination, release, and universal service. Old chapters close to make way for what is truly aligned with your soul.",love:"Relationships that no longer serve your highest self naturally complete. Those that remain are profoundly meaningful.",career:"Philanthropy, healing, arts, teaching, and global service call to you.",inner:"Practice forgiveness — of others, and most importantly, of yourself.",advice:"Let go of what is finished. The universe cannot bring the new until you release the old with gratitude."},
